('24th Annual Run to Remember', 'Run to Remember', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">Cadets,</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">The 24th Annual Run to Remember will be taking place on Saturday, 14 September at 0900. &nbsp;This 5K run is held every year in support of all MIAs and POWs with all proceeds going toward the Wounded Warrior Project. &nbsp;Run to Remember honors RPI graduate 1Lt Jon Kohl who survived a helicopter crash while he was deployed to Afghanistan. &nbsp;The Wounded Warrior Project has profoundly impacted the Kohl family and continues to provide support to other heroes like 1Lt Kohl. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">Share the registration link and flyer with family members, friends, and anyone else who you think might be interested. &nbsp;The second page is attached to the flyer to provide more information on the purpose of the run. &nbsp;All cadets should be at the race - either running or volunteering. &nbsp;If you are not able to participate or volunteer on the day of the race, please reach out to me with your prior commitment. &nbsp;I hope to see you all there! &nbsp;If you have any questions, feel free to contact me. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">Registration Link :&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://runtoremember.redpodium.com/run-to-remember-2019\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">https://runtoremember.redpodium.com/run-to-remember-2019</span> </span></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Vkky_rW0KEFR5cV7_yHqEQjj0S6GWSYT/view?usp=sharing\">Volunteer Spreadsheet</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://rpi.box.com/s/sihhp9wazygipixap5li61k6uba1gzwh\">2019 Flyer</a></p>\r\n<pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; overflow: auto; color: #333333; padding: 0px; caret-color: #333333; white-space: pre-wrap !important;\"><span class=\"sig\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />-- \r\nVery Respectfully,\r\n\r\nSTEPHANIE R. HAND, C/Capt, AFROTC\r\nCommander, Training Support Squadron\r\n550th AFROTC Training Support Squadron\r\nhands@rpi.edu\r\n(518)-683-3507</span></pre>', 17, 16, '2019-09-04 19:22:51', NULL);
