('Detachment Fall Picnic', 'Detachment Fall Picnic', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Cadets,</span></p>\r\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-6d60a8bf-7fff-80d3-5f77-7d88cf3d196e\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">AS 100 and AS 250 cadets welcome to Detachment 550! AS 200s and POC welcome back! At the start of each semester Moral, Welfare, and Recreation (MWR) Flight hosts an informal event to encourage the integration of our new members into the Cadet Wing. </span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">This semester we will be having a picnic at </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Prospect Park</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> on </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Saturday, September 14, 2019, </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">from</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> 1100 to 1400. </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">This is promptly after the Run to Remember, and I encouraged cadets to participate in or volunteer for the run before coming to the park for food and games. The park is about a 15-minute walk from the RPI Armory or about a 5-minute drive. If you plan to attend, please fill out </span><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScfdH-S6bBS29MBeo_46EGMlC0Fthxj4wf2Gdy9fbqmDSq4PA/viewform?usp=sf_link\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #1155cc; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">THIS FORM</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> and pay me $5.00 cash or Venmo (@hannahenggasser) by COB Friday, September 13, 2019, to cover the cost of food and drinks.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">This is a non-mandatory but SUPER FUN event, and you should be wearing civilian attire if you choose to attend.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Very Respectfully,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">HANNAH J. ENGGASSER</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, C/2nd Lt, AFROTC</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Commander, MWR Flight</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">550th AFROTC Support Squadron</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">enggah@rpi.edu</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(215)313-9983</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 74, 17, '2019-09-04 21:14:56', NULL),
('Fundraising Opportunity', 'Tarps in the Armory', '<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #626f82; font-family: monospace; font-size: 15px; background-color: #f7f7f7;\">Cadets,<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />There is a great opportunity to get some volunteer hours and help out the Detachment. I have attached a spreadsheet with sign up times if you are interested. Every little bit helps!<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: #f7f7f7; color: #0773a6; text-decoration-line: none; font-family: monospace; font-size: 15px;\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1JAu99_KXkbz1cp-82UFY3LQLdGKp3ixbfX71J5iUCbE/edit?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1JAu99_KXkbz1cp-82UFY3LQLdGKp3ixbfX71J5iUCbE/edit?usp=sharing</a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #626f82; font-family: monospace; font-size: 15px; background-color: #f7f7f7;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />If you have any issues, feel free to ask me.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Very Respectfully,<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />IAN A. MORIARTY, C/2d Lt, AFROTC<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Special Projects Flight Commander<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />550th AFROTC Mission Support Group</span></p>\r\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: #f7f7f7; color: #0773a6; text-decoration-line: none; font-family: monospace; font-size: 15px;\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"mailto:hofmaj2@rpi.edu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">moriai@rpi.edu</a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #626f82; font-family: monospace; font-size: 15px; background-color: #f7f7f7;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></span>(413) 824-5286</p>', 20, 18, '2019-09-05 00:19:12', NULL),
('24th Annual Run to Remember', 'Run to Remember', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">The 24th Annual Run to Remember will be taking place on Saturday, 14 September at 0900. &nbsp;This 5K run is held every year in support of all MIAs and POWs with all proceeds going toward the Wounded Warrior Project. &nbsp;Run to Remember honors RPI graduate 1Lt Jon Kohl who survived a helicopter crash while he was deployed to Afghanistan. &nbsp;The Wounded Warrior Project has profoundly impacted the Kohl family and continues to provide support to other heroes like 1Lt Kohl. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">Share the registration link and flyer with family members, friends, and anyone else who you think might be interested. &nbsp;The second page is attached to the flyer to provide more information on the purpose of the run. &nbsp;All cadets should be at the race - either running or volunteering. &nbsp;If you are not able to participate or volunteer on the day of the race, please reach out to me with your prior commitment. &nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fdff00;\">Register or sign up to volunteer by COB Thursday 12 September.</span><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"> &nbsp;</span></span>I hope to see you all there! &nbsp;If you have any questions, feel free to contact me. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: bo