('24th Annual Run to Remember', 'Run to Remember', '<h5 class=\"card-title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 1.25rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';\">Run to Remember</h5>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">The 24th Annual Run to Remember will be taking place on Saturday, 14 September at 0900. &nbsp;This 5K run is held every year in support of all MIAs and POWs with all proceeds going toward the Wounded Warrior Project. &nbsp;Run to Remember honors RPI graduate 1Lt Jon Kohl who survived a helicopter crash while he was deployed to Afghanistan. &nbsp;The Wounded Warrior Project has profoundly impacted the Kohl family and continues to provide support to other heroes like 1Lt Kohl. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">Share the registration link and flyer with family members, friends, and anyone else who you think might be interested. &nbsp;The second page is attached to the flyer to provide more information on the purpose of the run. &nbsp;All cadets should be at the race - either running or volunteering. &nbsp;If you are not able to participate or volunteer on the day of the race, please reach out to me with your prior commitment. &nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: #f1c40f;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: #fdff00;\">Register or sign up to volunteer by COB Thursday 12 September.</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>I hope to see you all there! &nbsp;If you have any questions, feel free to contact me. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">Registration Link :&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://runtoremember.redpodium.com/run-to-remember-2019\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">https://runtoremember.redpodium.com/run-to-remember-2019</span> </span></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Vkky_rW0KEFR5cV7_yHqEQjj0S6GWSYT/view?usp=sharing\">Volunteer Spreadsheet</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-syst