('PT 4', 'PT 4', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://rpi.app.box.com/s/t22djoaa9dur3vqmnbofn4wskvige7ib\">PT 4</a> will be taking place on Thursday, September 12th from 0630 - 0730 at the Armory. We will be performing a Murph Challenge, stretch accoringly and be sure to stay well hydrated</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br />Very Respectfully,<br /><br />PHU T. THAI, C/3C, AFROTC<br />Alpha Flight<br />550th AFROTC Training Support Squadron<br />thaip@rpi.edu<br />(315) 420-7868</p>', 5, 28, '2019-09-10 18:50:30', NULL),
('Website Outages and Other Bugs', 'Website Outages and Bugs', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>As you all know, this website is relatively new and new features are being pushed out on a regular basis. If you have any ideas regarding helpful features/design changes, please send me a message on GroupMe or an email with such.</p>\r\n<p>In addition to this, the RPI Union websites have been having occasional outage issues, so the website may be down sporadically. Cyber Flight is currently looking into solutions to this.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your flexibility and understanding</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>KATHERINE G. DONOVAN, C/2d Lt, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Cyber Flight Commander</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Communications Squadron&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>donovk5@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>(847) 682-0262</p>', 11, 29, '2019-09-10 19:16:13', NULL),
('Website Memorandum Standardization and Instructions', 'Memos', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>All memorandums will now be submitted through the website unless otherwise specified. This includes all excused and unexcused PMT events.</p>\r\n<p>Memos will still be written formerly using the same template that can be found in the <a href=\"https://onedrive.live.com/?authkey=%21AJPa0eTlsQ64xlg&amp;cid=3825622D1AC56C93&amp;id=3825622D1AC56C93%211011&amp;parId=3825622D1AC56C93%21967&amp;o=OneUp\">OneDrive.</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Steps to submit a memo:</p>\r\n<p>1. Under More, select&nbsp; \'View Event Attendance\'</p>\r\n<p>2. Select the event that was missed under \'Select Event\'; for normal memo submissions select \'Memo Submission\'</p>\r\n<p>3. Under \'Memo Reason\' select the reason why you missed the event or \'Non-Attendance\' for non-attendance related memos</p>\r\n<p>4. Enter only the LAST name of the cadet who requested the memo under \'For Cadet\'</p>\r\n<p>5. Attach a PDF of your memo including any doctors notes, do NOT submit any file type other than a PDF</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This information will also be posted under documentation.</p>\r\n<p>Please keep in mind that this is a new function to the website and bugs can still occur.</p>\r\n<p>If you have any questions, comments, concerns, or suggestions, don\'t hesitate to reach out to me or another member of Cyber Flight.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>KATHERINE G. DONOVAN, C/2d Lt, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Cyber Flight Commander</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Communications Squadron&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>donovk5@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>(847) 682-0262</p>', 11, 30, '2019-09-10 19:16:20', NULL),
('IG Update', 'Initial Counselings & Hair Standards', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cadets,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Initial counselings are here and for 100s are due COB October 1st. For all other cadets they are due COB September 15th. Please submit these up your chain of command and your direct superiors will be in contact with you to schedule a time to meet for this.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Also, your hair must be in regulation before October 1st for new cadets. The rules for this can be found in the AFI 36-23. For example, men must not have hair touching their ears and no longer than an inch on the top.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Counseling Form Link: <a title=\"AF724\" href=\"https://1drv.ms/b/s!ApNsxRotYiU4h3Qaj1bIUG_ymcj2?e=nxjeSe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AF724</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">AFI Link: <a title=\"AFI\" href=\"https://1drv.ms/b/s!ApNsxRotYiU4h3UG3atv2Y52qejz?e=gnXg9x\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AFI 36-2903</a></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>NOTE: This message must be Read and Understood by COB 13 September 19.</p>\r\n<div style=\"caret-color: #000000; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">--</span><br class=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Very Respectfully,</span><br class=\"\" /><br class=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">JOSEPH W. MESSARE, C/Lt Col,&nbsp;AFROTC</span><br class=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Inspector General</span><br class=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">550th Training Squadron</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"caret-color: #000000; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a class=\"\" href=\"mailto:messaj@rpi.edu\">messaj@rpi.edu</a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"caret-color: #000000; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(585) 500-9728</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 2, 31, '2019-09-11 14:48:48', NULL),
('9/11 Inspirational Videos', 'Inspiration', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Here are links to the two videos Lt Col Grahm mentioned in LLab.</p>\r\n<p>George Bush 9/11 Rubble Speech:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x7OCgMPX2mE&amp;t=10s\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x7OCgMPX2mE&amp;t=10s</a></p>\r\n<p>Phillis USA Chant:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvpBivJBK7o\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvpBivJBK7o</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>--&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>KATHERINE G. DONOVAN, C/2d Lt, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Cyber Flight Commander</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Communications Squadron&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>donovk5@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>(847) 682-0262</p>', 11, 32, '2019-09-11 15:34:02', NULL),
