('24th Annual Run to Remember', 'Run to Remember Volunteer Information', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">The 24th Annual Run to Remember will be taking place on Saturday, 14 September at 0900 at ECAV. &nbsp;Volunteers who signed up for set-up, registration tables, or timing should arrive at 0700. &nbsp;If you are a road guard, arrive at 0745 to hear more about your position. &nbsp;If you are registered to run for the race, you should arrive no later than 0830.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">UOD : ABUs - If you have not been issued ABUs, the UOD is PTGs.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">There are still spots open for road guard stations on the volunteer spreadsheet, so be sure to sign up if you do not have a position. &nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: #f1c40f;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: #fdff00;\">Register or sign up to volunteer by COB TODAY.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>If you have any questions, feel free to co