('Cornell Drill Meet', 'Cornell Drill Meet', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Cadets,</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">The Cornell Military Excellence Competition is coming up soon and will be held on 19 October 2019. The events that you can sign up for are the 4x400 relay, 5K run, Ironman, 4x100 freestyle swim, 4x100 IM relay, and a 50 yard indiviual freestyle swim. There is also a Fitness Medley and the explanation for this can be found on the link below. Please take a look at the spreadsheet and fill out what events you want to do by October 2nd COB so I can pass along the information to Cornell. For transportation, you will have to figure out a carpool to get to Cornell. We have had great participation at the Cornell Meet in the past so lets keep that up this year.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple C