('Military Appreciation Football Game', 'Military Appreciation Football Game', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Tomorrow is the Military Appreciation Football Game! This is a completely locked off environment where you can learn more about each other and have fun. If you wish to attend, please arrive at the RPI East Campus Stadium at 1800 where I will give you your admission ticket as well as a coupon for a free meal at the concession stand. Please note: <strong>There is no UOD for this event. You may wear civilian attire.</strong> In addition there are a lot of extra tickets, so it is fine if you did not have me reserve one for you and would still like to attend. Arnold Air Society and Silver Wings will have tables set up inside the ECAV Concourse, so consider helping them out!</p>\r\n<p>The game begins at 1800 and will end at 2100. I hope to see you all there!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>ERJIN CHOI, C/2d Lt, AFROTC<br />Joint Service Representative<br />550th AFROTC Cadet Wing<br />choie@rpi.edu<br />(516) 840-1288</p>', 33, 47, '2019-09-20 21:42:52', NULL),
('LLAB 4 Car Pool List', 'Car Pool List', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This upcoming LLAB will be taking place at UAlbany. A carpool list has been made so cadets can be sure to have a ride to and from UAlbany. This carpool list must be filled out by everyone, even if you are a UAlbany student. This must be filled out by Tuesday COB. All IMT and FTP cadets that are attending the morning flight meetings must ride with someone that is going to the flight meetings. That being said if you are driving to the flight meetings in the morning make sure to designate your car as a flight meeting car in someway.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X0UNEXNm-ce_K9IKaAc7dlRNHPAIJlxULACuEPLTw_g/edit?usp=sharing\">Car Pool List</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>BAILEY E. DAIGLE, C/2d Lt, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Alpha Flight Commander</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Training Squadron</p>\r\n<p>daiglb@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>(518)742-0980</p>', 40, 48, '2019-09-21 17:26:58', NULL),
