('LLAB 4', 'LLAB 4', '<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Cadets,</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Operation: New Surroundings</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Date: 25 September</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Location: SEFCU Arena Entrance</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Time: 0800</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; color: #404040; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">UOD:&nbsp; The Uniform of the Day (UOD) will be the </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; color: #404040; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Airman Battle Uniform</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; color: #404040; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> (ABU).&nbsp; Cadets who have not been issued the ABUs will wear </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; color: #404040; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Black Polo and Khakis </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; color: #404040; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(BPaK) or </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; color: #404040; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Detachment Polo and Khakis </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numer