('Schindler\'s School of Swiftness', 'SSS', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>I would like to get SSS started soon this semester. For those of you who don\'t know, SSS is a great opportunity to improve run times for the PFA, meet more cadets outside of LLAB and PT, and have fun doing running workouts with others. This year SSS is going to be a little different. There will only be one meeting time a week for one hour and we will exclusively be doing hard track workouts to help cadets improve PFA run times. If you are interested please fill out the When is Good below by Monday COB so we can get the workouts rolling. All are welcome, please message me if you have questions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>http://whenisgood.net/efpysdn</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>SPENCER C. SCHINDLER, C/Lt Col, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Operations Group Commander</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Operations Group&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>schins@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>(845)417-6930</p>', 43, 57, '2019-09-27 03:45:50', NULL),
