('Grooming Standards', 'Final Reminder on Hair & Grooming Standards', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times;\">Cadets,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times;\">As a final reminder your hair must be in regs by October 1st (our next upcoming PT session). If you are not in regs you will be sent home no questions asked. That means no hair touching the ears and no longer than an inch on the top and a clean shave for men. Please review the AFI if you are unclear as to the standards.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times;\">AFI Link: <a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0056b3; background-color: #ffffff;\" title=\"AFI\" href=\"https://static.e-publishing.af.mil/production/1/af_a1/publication/afi36-2903/afi36-2903.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AFI 36-2903</a></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Read and Understood by: COB 2 October 2019</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\