('LLAB 5', 'LLAB 5', '<p>Cadets,<br /><br />Operation:&nbsp; <strong>Do You Know the Way?</strong><br /><br />Date:&nbsp; <strong>2 October</strong><br /><br />Location:&nbsp; <strong>RPI Tech Park</strong><br /><br />Time:&nbsp; <strong>0750</strong><br /><br /><br />UOD:&nbsp; The Uniform of the Day (UOD) will be the Airman Battle Uniform (ABU).&nbsp; Cadets who have not been issued ABUs will wear civilian clothes.&nbsp; Cadets will be traveling on uneven terrain, so durable footwear is recommended.&nbsp; Please remember to dress warmly, as morning temperatures are expected to be cool.<br /><br />Operation Do You Know the Way? will consist of a land navigation briefing and demonstration, followed by GLPs.&nbsp; Cadets will meet at the 42nd Infantry Division parking lot.<br /><br /><br />OPORD:&nbsp; <a title=\"OPORD\" href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1QhMX66asffUqlaP0IqdSrVMjBZZuVzzk\">OPORD</a><br /><br /><br />Very Respectfully,<br /><br /><br />ALEXANDER T. FERENCZHALMY, C/3C, AFROTC<br /><br />Alpha Flight<br /><br />550th AFROTC Training Squadron<br /><br />ferena@rpi.edu<br /><br />(575) 921-9403</p>', 14, 62, '2019-09-29 17:30:11', NULL),
