('PT 10', 'PT 10', '<p>Cadets,&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://rpi.app.box.com/s/oqtgiju5vruzax127nvohf2wprr1magw\">PT 10</a> will be on Wednesday, October 2nd,&nbsp; from 0630-0700, at the Glenmore Road Armory at 0630. Please arrive NLT 0620. PT will consist of a calisthenics workout run by Cadet Messare. UOD will be Airman Battle Uniforms (ABUs) or appropriate civilian clothes. For those cadets, not issued ABUs, keep in mind that there will not be a place to change, so dress accordingly. Wear outer layers that can be easily taken off for PT and put back on for LLAB. Be sure to hydrate and stretch prior to PT.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>JOHN S. ROGERS, C/2nd Lt, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Commander, Bravo Flight</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Training Squadron</p>\r\n<p>rogerj9@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>603-748-6495</p>', 26, 67, '2019-09-30 21:49:51', NULL),
