('Car Pool LLAB 5', 'Car Pool LLAB 5', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times;\">Cadets,</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times;\">This upcoming LLAB will take place at the 42nd Infantry Division (Glenmore Road Armory). A carpool list has been made so cadets can be sure to have a ride to and from the 42nd Infantry Division. This carpool list must be filled out by everyone. All Cadets must arrive by 0620. PT will begin at 0630. If you have an exam, please make note of that on this car pool sheet. Furthermore, if you need to leave early make sure you sign up in the appropriate column. This must be filled out by Tuesday COB.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><a title=\"Car Pool Sign Up\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NmpwdinpVT4VhGSq9AihFjGSME4ihU8Vam3qKHE1v7A/edit#gid=0\">Car Pool Sign Up</a><br /><br /><br />Very Respectfully,<br /><br /><br />ALEXANDER T. FERENCZHALMY<br /><br />Alpha Flight<br /><br />550th AFROTC Training Squadron<br /><br />ferena@rpi.edu<br /><br />(575) 921-9403</p>', 14, 70, '2019-10-01 18:56:01', NULL),
('PT 11', 'PT 11', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QhMX66asffUqlaP0IqdSrVMjBZZuVzzk/view?usp=sharing\">PT 11</a> will be on Thursday, 3 October, from 0630 to 0730.&nbsp; We will be doing a weight room safety course.&nbsp; The plan for PT will follow the original plan for PT 6.&nbsp; Remember to keep up on water, electrolytes, and stretching.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>MICHAEL F. SWEENEY, C/3C, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>General Military Course Advisor</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Cadet Wing</p>\r\n<p>sweenm2@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>(518)530-8696</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 16, 71, '2019-10-01 23:56:28', NULL),
('Fund Requests', 'Financial', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This post will be an outline for the fund request/reimbursment process for detachment activities. Read &amp; Understand <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>NLT</strong></span> 7 October 2019.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Fund requests will be send directly to me by email <strong>(leew15@rpi.edu)</strong> once you have finalized figures and details of the event with your superior (i.e. if you were in MWR flight, get it approved with the MWR commander). Please make sure that it is thourough, detailed, and formatted enough for record. For any reimbursements, I need copies of receipts for all purchases to ensure that you get your money back so save receipts and do not lose them.</p>\r\n<p>Fund requests should be sent <strong>no later than two weeks</strong> in advance for an event. This is because a large source of our funds is held by RPI, and processing through them takes some time. Any fund requests made after this time will be denied unless there is a good reason. Additionally, if you spend money before getting approval for a reimbursement request you will not be reimbursed.&nbsp;As long as you are actively updating me about the event plans and discussing potential options prior to sending the final memo there shouldn\'t be any problems.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Notes about funds</span>:</p>\r\n<p>As mentioned before, a bulk of the money (~$700) is in the RPI account, but it can be limiting because it can only be used on RPI approved companies (i.e. Pizza, clothing merch, etc). Volunteering opportunities that are posted here for Sodexo will bring in the money for this account.</p>\r\n<p>The Cadet Fund account is the most flexible, however it only has ~$150 remaining,. Speak with me if you would like to help fundraise for this account. If we fundraise it will not be in uniform and not displayed that we are cadets (like a booster club) since we are not authorized to fundraise in the name of AFROTC.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong><a style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\" href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1zrekKjpKtWFJ3PffdlprOpaU23089MJw/view?usp=sharing\">Example Fund Request Memo</a></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Also please make sure emails are sent to <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">leew15@rpi.edu</span>, another Lee at RPI keeps getting my ROTC emails, so don\'t miss your 2 week cutoff by sending it elsewhere.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>--</p>\r\n<p>LEE BRIAN, C/2d Lt, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Director of Training</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Training Support Squadron</p>\r\n<p>leew15@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>(914) 574-7732</p>', 10, 72, '2019-10-02 02:17:06', NULL),
('PT 11', 'PT 11', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Cadets,</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QhMX66asffUqlaP0IqdSrVMjBZZuVzzk/view?usp=sharing\">PT 11</a>&nbsp;will be on Thursday, 3 October, from 0630 to 0730.&nbsp; We will be doing a weight room safety course.&nbsp; The plan for PT will follow the original plan for PT 6.&nbsp; Remember to keep up on water, electrolytes, and stretching.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sa