('LLAB 7 Feedback', 'LLAB Feedback', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Please take a few minutes to fill out the following survey. By filling out this survey you are helping Operations Group gauge how to plan LLAB better so that they are more enjoyable while providing the training environment we need. This feedback is important for us so we can continuosly improve and end the semester on a great note. Thank you.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfyrHmKmCQTNGCG3SCEOcT6fFPPqED52hL5jy9y3x-YiSj84w/viewform?usp=sf_link\">Survey</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Read and Understood by: Optional</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Repectfully,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>BAILEY E. DAIGLE, C/2d Lt, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Commander, Alpha Flight</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Training Squadron</p>\r\n<p>daiglb@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>(518)742-0980</p>', 40, 94, '2019-10-16 15:55:27', NULL),
('LLAB 10 Officer Panel Interest', 'LLAB 10', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>LLAB 10 on November 6th will consist of an officer panel where we will have the chance to listen to officers speak about their military and leadership experience. We will also have the chance to ask these officers questions throughout the panel. Please fill out the survey below when you get the chance so I can reach out to officers with experience in career fields that we are all interested in so we can get the most out of this panel.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf_q5dphEbWaFXAxYI4EIA3YkeOO8DzsbH0JDxrdO_Rpys92g/viewform?usp=sf_link\">Survey</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Read and Understood by: 19 October 2019</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>BAILEY E. DAIGLE, C/2d Lt, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Commander, Alpha Flight</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Training Squadron</p>\r\n<p>daiglb@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>(518)742-0980</p>', 40, 95, '2019-10-16 17:33:34', NULL),
('Taylor Trophy', 'Event Sign-up', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>We will be having Taylor Trophy on Sunday, October 27th. This is a joint service event where each ROTC branch compete against one other in various sporting events to obtain the titular Taylor Trophy at the end of the year. This semester, we will be playing ultimate frisbee, flag football, and tug of war. <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NhAaCnpYlfIgL4w-gRPMPj3iJZfLzDHQOy0GaD0K820/edit?usp=sharing\">Click here to sign up for your preferred event.</a> You may also volunteer as the Air Force referee for ultimate frisbee and football on the same Google Sheet.</p>\r\n<p>In addition, you may sign up for multiple events as no two events will coincide. The date, time, location, and uniform is all written in the document. Specific rules for each event will be posted at a later date.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">ERJIN CHOI, C/2d Lt, AFROTC<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Joint Service Representative<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />550th AFROTC Cadet Wing<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />choie@rpi.edu<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />(516)840-1288</p>', 33, 96, '2019-10-16 19:18:46', NULL);
