('Taylor Trophy (Information Update)', 'Event Sign-up and Location Change', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Cadets,</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">We will be having Taylor Trophy on Sunday, October 27th at the <strong>Harkness Track &amp; Field</strong>. This is a joint service event where each ROTC branch compete against one other in various sporting events to obtain the titular Taylor Trophy at the end of the year. This semester, we will be playing ultimate frisbee, flag football, and tug of war.&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NhAaCnpYlfIgL4w-gRPMPj3iJZfLzDHQOy0GaD0K820/edit?usp=sharing4w-gRPMPj3iJZfLzDHQOy0GaD0K820/edit?usp=sharing\">Click here to sign up for your preferred event.</a> You may also volunteer as the Air Force referee for ultimate frisbee and football on the same Google Sheet. In addition, you may sign up for multiple events as no two events will coincide.<br /><br />Ultimate Frisbee: 1000-1115<br />Tug of War: 1120-1200<br />Flag Football: 1200-1400<br /><br />We only need a few more participants in each event to have enough players to compete, so please sign up as soon as possible.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -appl