('Hockey Game Recruiting', 'Hockey Game Recruiting', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>There will be a recruiting table set up at the hockey game this Saturday 9 November from 19:00-22:00 and two spots are available for volunteering to sit: 19:00-19:30, 19:30-20:00.</p>\r\n<p>UOD: ABUs, cadets who have not been issued ABUs will wear polo and khakis.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you are interested in filling one of these spots please fill in the Google Sheet linked below. If you have any problems or concerns please contact myself, Cadet Hofmann.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Il9kmSNafOxH_uN4BvXZfrl7AjAvq6ODVCgVMUugrnc/edit?usp=sharing\">Link</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #212529; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; caret-color: #212529; background-color: #ffffff;\">Read and Understood by: Optional</span></p>\r\n<p>--</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>JAMES W. HOFMANN, C/3C, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Special Projects Flight</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Cadet Wing</p>', 13, 114, '2019-11-07 18:38:44', NULL),
('Military Appreciation Hockey Game', 'Hockey Game Information', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Cadets,</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Tomorrow from 1900-2100 at the Houston Field House will be the Military Appreciation Hockey Game. Uniforms are not mandatory but everyone is encouraged to wear morale apparel. If you do arrive in uniform or bring a CAC card, you may attend the game for free and receive free concessions. In addition, Joint Service will be raising money for the Veterans Miracle Center in Albany. This is a store that offers clothing and everyday necessities to veterans and active-duty at no charge. This organization is especially helpful for wounded veterans in the Albany area who may be on a fixed income. Consider bringing money to donate to this fantastic cause.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">There will also be designated seating if you obtained your ticket through me, so please refer to <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/17Z6iJuL42szsKVTO1Nr9q85eFFRjy8yxQu_FU_xWR3U/edit?usp=sharing\">this spreadsheet</a> to see which area you are in. However if there is enough room elsewhere, feel free to move.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Lastly, I need five volunteers to help collect funds for charity. You will only be actively working in-between periods, so you will not miss the game if you wish to help. If you want to assist in collecting charity funds, send me a message and await additional information about your duties. Please think about helping, I will greatly appreciate it and you will be raising money for a noteworthy charity.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">I hope to see you all there! It will be a lot of fun and there will be some cool special events that will happen during the game!</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">ERJIN CHOI, C/2d Lt, AFROTC<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Joint Service Representative<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />550th AFROTC Cadet Wing<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />choie@rpi.edu<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />(516)840-1288</p>', 33, 115, '2019-11-09 01:51:20', NULL),
