('Final Counseling', 'Final Counseling', '<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: 12pt;\">Cadets,</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times; font-size: 12pt;\">As we are at the end of the year we will be doing final counselings. These counselings will be done with your immediate superiors and then sent up the chain of command. The official deadline to submit your final counseling by is NLT COB 6 Dec 19. When sending your couselings up the chain wait to aggregate all counselings to send at once as to prevent multiple disjointed emails. Counseling files are to be titled LASTNAME_FINAL_COUNSELING_F19.pdf. Contact your chain of command with further questions.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times;\">--<br />Very Respectfully,<br /><br />JOSEPH W. MESSARE, C/Lt Col,&nbsp;AFROTC<br />Inspector General<br />550th Training Squadron</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times;\"><a style=\"color: #954f72;\" title=\"mailto:messaj@rpi.edu\" href=\"mailto:messaj@rpi.edu\"><span style=\"color: #0563c1;\">messaj@rpi.edu</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times;\">(585) 500-9728</span></p>', 2, 122, '2019-11-25 02:02:56', NULL),
('MWR Secret Santa', 'MWR Secret Santa', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>As the school year is ending MWR is organizing one last event for cadets to get together and enjoy the holidays with a Det 550 Secret Santa on 6 December 2019. This is an optional event, but for those who are intrested should sign up in the link below. The last day to sign up will be Wednesday the 27th at midnight. The price limit will be $10-20 dollars or whatever you are comfortable with. Cadets will be selected through a random generator and told who they recieved no later than Friday the 29th. I encourage everyone to sign up to hang out as a det on last time before the holidays.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Sign up sheet: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/135PtTrHCtPpZZ-lhNOKnnrd7LITsiD0qGiw-Fhk8PzI/edit?usp=sharing\">Secret Santa</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Very Respectfully,</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">NIALL E. RODGERS, C/3C, AFROTC</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-siz