('GMC/POC Ice Skating', 'GMC/POC Ice Skating', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This semester\'s GMC/POC event is ice skating at Hudson Valley Community College!&nbsp; This will be a fun opportunity to socialize and decompress at the close of the semester, so please plan on attending.&nbsp; Fill out <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfB5XTCDNMiMv-cKi0dJfSLrfqhFy3YMh25LF_Jc3r3vTSRtw/viewform?usp=sf_link\">this survey</a> by <strong>COB Friday, 6 December&nbsp;</strong>to help me determine which day is best.&nbsp; Even if you cannot attend, please fill out the survey and select \"I cannot attend\".&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully.</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; white-space: pre-wrap !important;\"><span class=\"sig\" style=\"color: #666666; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">MICHAEL F. SWEENEY, C/3C, AFROTC\r\nGeneral Military Course Advisor\r\n550th AFROTC Cadet Wing\r\n<a style=\"color: #0186ba;\" href=\"mailto:sweenm2@rpi.edu\">sweenm2@rpi.edu</a>\r\n(518)530-8696</span></pre>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 16, 124, '2019-12-02 21:52:41', NULL),
