('ROTC Cadet Appreciation Basketball Game', 'RPI vs. Clarkson - Cadet Appreciation Game', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This Saturday at 1600 will be the RPI vs. Clarkson ROTC Cadet Appreciation Basketball Game and will take place inside the Houston Field House. Wear either the ABU or DetPaK for this event. This is a special occasion where RPI recognizes and highlights the extra efforts ROTC cadets take to balance challenging course work and general college life while undergoing vigorous self-improvement through military training and giving back to the community via volunteering events. To say thank you, RPI will allow ROTC cadets to attend the game and recieve food and drinks completely free of charge. This is a great time for you and your classmates to relax and enjoy a basketball game to recuperate before wrapping up the school semester and preparing for finals week. This may even be the last time some of you can hang out with your fellow cadets outside of LLAB.</p>\r\n<p>I will be using the \"Read and Understood\" button to gauge interest so I can tell RPI staff how much food to bring for the event. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">By clicking on \"Read and Understood\" on this announcement, you are saying that you will be attending.<br /><br /></span>I highly encourage everyone to attend and I hope I will see you all there.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>ERJIN CHOI, C/2d Lt, AFROTC<br />Joint Service Representative<br />550th AFROTC Cadet Wing<br />choie@rpi.edu<br />(516)840-1288</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 33, 129, '2019-12-04 21:43:38', NULL),
('Volunteer Opportunities', 'Volunteer Opportunities', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Cadets,</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">There are several volunteering opportunities coming up that would greatly support Detachment 550 that I would like to bring to your attention.&nbsp; Volunteering to help at these events will directly gain money to fund activities for the Wing.&nbsp; These events will be taking place on Thursday December 12 and Friday December 13. More detailed information can be found in the sign up sheet I have listed below, describing times and locations.&nbsp; I highly encourage each cadet to participate if you are available!</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>