('GMC/POC Ice Skating', 'GMC/POC Ice Skating', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Cadets,</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Based of the results of the survey, the GMC/POC Ice Skating event will be this Friday, 13 December, from 1200 to 1400 at Hudson Valley Community College\'s Conway Ice Rink! The Conway Ice Rink is located in the McDonough Sports Complex, which has free parking out front.&nbsp; Admission is $5 and skate rentals are available for an additional $3.&nbsp; We can get a group discount of $1 off everybody if we have more than 10 people come.&nbsp; I hope you can attend this event, it will be a fun way to decompress and socialize.&nbsp; Also, feel free to bring friends or family along, the more the merrier!&nbsp; Please send me a message on GroupMe by <strong>COB Tuesday, 10 December, </strong>if you would like to attend.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto,