(82, '129.161.112.9', '661622412', '$2y$12$OZTPZPSVzXAmhqW4XRFiiOCasr0RHqS3t9SCI0mI0gi0MSrLAylOq', 'woodsa2@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1567019103, 1578443288, 1, 'Andrew', 'Woods', 'AS400', '5188521521', NULL, 'Aeronautical Engineering', 'What was your childhood nickname?', 'cadet', '<p>Born and bred here in Albany NY, making me about 20 minutes from home.&nbsp; That being said, I go home to see my family whenever I get the chance pending I have no upcoming exams or ROTC events.&nbsp; I am the middle of three brothers, whom I consider myself to be close to.&nbsp; One is 23 living in LA, the other is 16 a sophomore in high school.&nbsp; I am most definitely an outdoor enthusiast.&nbsp; If I have the time/money I\'d be skiing or hiking everyday.&nbsp; I am a firm believer in delayed gratification; however, I recognize the importance of enjoying the present on the road to success.&nbsp; I never played tennis but I am a big Roger Federer fan who said \"there\'s no way around hard work, embrace it.\"</p>', '<p>- Set the example for work that goes above in beyond in the detachment</p>\r\n<p>- Be approachable and relatable&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>- Run as a study break to score sub 10 on the PFA</p>', '<p>- Talk to my family on the phone every other day</p>\r\n<p>- Check my phone once every 30 minutes during study time</p>\r\n<p>- Attend office hours once a week for each class</p>', 'Foxtrot', 'Cadet', 'Vice Wing Commander', '<p>- Detachment 550 Warrior Spirit</p>', NULL, '82.PNG', 0),
(83, '129.161.112.9', '661801613', '$2y$12$gK7Pf/ZSay/oXi0BwH2Zb.2qT.ww9i9gqjcjnoQ7UV5Rsp1SPrPpm', 'perryi3@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1567021124, 1578595488, 1, 'Isabell', 'Perry', 'AS400', '9148605958', 21313, 'Economics and Mathematics', 'What is your favorite movie?', 'The Lion King', '<p>I am from Westchester, New York, and am currently a senior at Williams College. &nbsp;I play field hockey and lacrosse. &nbsp;I\'m also extremely interested in hiking and swimming.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Get an A in Air and Space Studies</p>\r\n<p>- Max out the PFA</p>\r\n<p>- Attend as many detachment events as possible</p>', '<p>- Attain a 3.5 semester GPA</p>\r\n<p>- Win a NESCAC field hockey championship</p>\r\n<p>- Make my bed everyday</p>', 'Foxtrot', 'Cadet', 'Wing Commander', '<p>- Earned a pilot slot (2019)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '83.png', 0),
(85, '129.161.112.9', '661992885', '$2y$10$.gNlDx.x61fkJuGNujVTGOmhOHI6EWMZO6sMVYvKbLxyLLzyWPTZe', 'parkj22@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1567607235, 1578610286, 1, 'Jaeyoung', 'Park', 'AS250', '4802926385', NULL, 'Homeland Security', 'What was your childhood nickname?', 'Billy', '<p>I am from UAlbany majoring in Emergency Prep - Homeland Secutiry to be specific. I enjoy flying, or anything related to aviation in general. I take pride in being the only US-Military affilited person in my family.</p>', '<p>- Receive a pilot slot</p>\r\n<p>- Pass DODMERB</p>\r\n<p>- Earn scholarship</p>', '<p>- Maintain 4.0 GPA</p>\r\n<p>- Catch upto 200s by end of the semester</p>\r\n<p>- Run for student government</p>', 'Alpha', 'Cadet', 'N/A', '', 'HHeAQNtZM1XvvhqodZBw0gOk1wgDzUyMkcFL7uu7', '85.jpg', 0),
(86, '129.161.112.9', '661956017', '$2y$10$rTJQcC4vQlFGeLLIU/a9Wuxiys0Xc7PPDRvG0SAK/yB8OdC77rbIW', 'toskaa@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1567618697, 1578444153, 1, 'Anthony', 'Toskas', 'AS100', '3478690359', 27986, 'Aeronautical Engineering', 'In what town was your first job?', 'Douglaston', '<p>I\'m from New York City, attending RPI for Aeronautical Engineering. I love to swim and I am hoping to make the varsity team here at RPI. I am part of ROTC because I want to become a fighter pilot in the Air Force and then go on to work on propulsion systems.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>-Completely finish all PT workouts this year</p>\r\n<p>-Pass the AFOQT, qualifying to be a pilot</p>\r\n<p>-Finish a Murph Challenge</p>', '<p>-Make the RPI Varsity Swim Team</p>\r\n<p>-Qualify for NCAA B-cut for the 100-yard freestyle</p>\r\n<p>-Maintain a 3.5 GPA minimum</p>', 'Bravo', 'Cadet', 'N/A', '', NULL, '86.jpg', 0),
(87, '129.161.112.9', '661913101', '$2y$10$sIntUILfdQ1Zj9S5YGeF1uRuU6O/8vOQS.d9u8ahmAW3QIJHE3vtK', 'Straut@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1567618793, 1576339370, 1, 'Trevor', 'Straub', 'AS250', '9147156870', 22936, 'Mechanical Engineering', 'What was your favorite sport in high school?', 'Baseball', '<p><span style=\"color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">My name is Trevor Straub and I am from Corltandt Manor, NY. I was a multi-sport athlete in highschool playing baseball and basketball. I participated in student government and served my community as a Town of Cortlandt Parks and Recreation Advisory board member.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- Serve as an engineer in the Air Force</span></p>', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- Obtain a bachelors degree in Mechanical Engineering from RPI</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- Become a second lieutenant in the United States Air Force</p>', 'Alpha', 'Cadet', 'Cadet ', '', NULL, '87.jpg', 0),
(88, '129.161.112.9', '661983897', '$2y$10$lLzoUAc9uKhRUQB.W.6YteOxAlh2qr2TL1gH.v7wrBcllh8e293Fq', 'chenz27@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1567993122, 1578578391, 1, 'Zoey', 'Chen', 'AS100', '9293869501', 30532, 'Foreign Studies/Languages', 'In what town was your first job?', 'NYC', '<p>I was born on April 27, 2001, in Brooklyn and sent to China a year after birth. I lived and studied in China and took occasional trips to the US to visit my parents. In 2010, I settled in Queens, NY until senior year of high school when I moved to Manhattan. After high school ended, I moved to my current address in Philadelphia.</p>', '<p>- Receive a pilot slot.</p>\r\n<p>- Max out PFA</p>\r\n<p>- Not lose my HSSP</p>', '<p>Study abroad for at least one semester</p>\r\n<p>I want to be proficient in the three major East Asian languages: Mandarin, Japanese, and Korean.</p>\r\n<p>Maintain my GPA at above 3.5</p>', 'Bravo', 'Cadet', 'Cadet', '', NULL, '88.jpg', 0),
(90, '129.161.112.9', '661971804', '$2y$10$HE9AqSLMYErDAFPlsZa19.trd98aEI45qL9Mh/YjCb9DFQtWQQ0AK', 'rifflj@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1568057007, 1578546366, 1, 'Justin', 'Rifflard', 'AS100', '2032578254', 27965, 'Computer and Systems Engineering', 'What was your childhood nickname?', '123', '<p>Born and raised in Connecticut. I used to marching band and varsity tennis in high school. Now, my hobbies include tennis and video games. I want to get at least a degree in Computer and systems engineering from RPI, and maybe even a dual major.</p>', '<p>-I want to do more volunteer activities.</p>\r\n<p>-Earn a pilot slot.</p>\r\n<p>-Maybe join armed drill team.</p>', '<p>-I would like to maintain at least a 3.5 GPA</p>\r\n<p>-Earn at least a 90 on the PFA</p>\r\n<p>-I want to graduate with an engineering degree.</p>', 'Bravo', 'Cadet', 'N/A', '', NULL, '90.jpg', 0),
(92, '129.161.112.9', '661988299', '$2y$10$j7QtZZ59HeUubi0uTSdoJecz2jPQ7rG7YWEuFyck90LX0RdlCsQrO', 'leil@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1568210887, 1576911387, 1, 'Leon', 'Lei', 'AS250', '3479775017', 28408, 'Mechanical Engineering', 'What was your childhood nickname?', '123', '<p><span style=\"color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">I am relatively local, coming from NYC. I like to breakdance, play video games and watch movies. I just want to improve and reach new heights.</span></p>', '<p>-Max out PFA&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>-Never miss a class/pt session</p>\r\n<p>-To never give up</p>', '<p>-Get straight A\'s</p>\r\n<p>-Get to 135lbs without gaining body fat %</p>\r\n<p>-Learn more breakdance moves</p>', 'Bravo', 'Cadet', 'N/A', '', NULL, '92.JPG', 0),
(94, '129.161.112.9', '661984042', '$2y$10$6L7mpxEo2dM1oib9mzKn6OnW/a93ul3OmhRa4tsRdjlBfR28gGR5q', 'swensc@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1568216832, 1576525083, 1, 'Cooper', 'Swenson', 'AS100', '2035010941', 27720, 'Information Technology & Web Science ', 'What was your childhood nickname?', 'Swen', '<p>I\'m Cadet Swenson and I\'m from Brookfield, Connecticut. I\'m a big fan of motorsports, running, and videogames. I can also do a pretty good Kermit the Frog impression.</p>', '<p>- Achieve a sub 9 minute 1.5 mile run&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>- Aquire a 95 PFA score&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>- Get a Type 1 scholarship</p>', '<p>- Attain a GPA of 3.0 and above</p>\r\n<p>- Draw for 30 minutes everyday&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>- Check my Email 3 times a day&nbsp;</p>', 'Bravo', 'Cadet', 'N/A', '', NULL, '941.jpg', 0),
(95, '129.161.112.9', '661992908', '$2y$10$T6l/ZJIRUdlpFG1.IUSRaOFcOH9q6Q82WnJmXs1wMes1H2Fmz/d8K', 'pratcm@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1568291835, 1578449971, 1, 'Marquez', 'Pratcher', 'AS250', '3345078021', 29474, 'Criminal Justice MA', 'What was your childhood nickname?', '123', '<p>I\'m from the Bronx, NY and I am currently a graduate student at UAlbany pursuing a masters in criminal justice. I\'m a Real Madrid fan and enjoy watching European football clubs. I also especially enjoy traveling and experiencing new places.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Get up to speed with my flight&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>- Excell at FT at Maxwell AFB</p>\r\n<p>- Achieve a pilot slot&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Graduate with my Masters</p>\r\n<p>- Become a Pilot</p>\r\n<p>- Pursue a career as a Commercial Pilot</p>', 'Alpha', 'Cadet', 'N/A', '', NULL, '95.jpg', 0),
(97, '146.112.47.75', 'TemporaryRin', '$2y$10$qujr1OySuMuINYZWL9JiGO9tAfdhRPILD..moeDc90wYgR1S3B7UW', 'ikeh@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1568408203, 1578621943, 1, 'Holton', 'Ike', 'AS100', '6077317586', 29564, 'Environmental Science and Sustainability', 'What was your childhood nickname?', '123', '<p><span style=\"color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">I\'m from Horseheads, New York, about 2 hours away from Hartwick College. I enjoy hunting, fishing, and hiking outdoors. When I watch movies, action movies and sci-fi movies are my favorite genre, but I will occasionally watch a scary movie or two!</span></p>', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- Max out PFA</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- Earn my Dress Blues with my detachment class</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- Become the best officer I can be by the time I graduate college</p>', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- Qualify for NCAA Championships in more than one sport</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- Make the Dean\'s list</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- Improve my overrall physical fitness</p>', 'Bravo', 'Cadet', 'N/A', '<p><span style=\"color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">- HSSP Type 2 scholarship recipient</span></p>', NULL, '97.jpeg', 0),
(98, '146.112.47.81', '661986076', '$2y$10$xpPFdTZIfxmHhQMy5hXDPeAcZNRt9sC3WAuM2SOmpOyQPFqHu.ERm', 'doughs@rpi.edu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1568408455, 1572969744, 1, 'Sydney', 'Doughlin', 'AS100', '9548060105', NULL, 'Undeclared Engineering  ', 'What was your childhood nickname?', '123', '<p>I was born and raised in Miami, Florida. I attend Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute to recieve a bachelor in engineeing.</p>', '<p>To join the Air Force as an engineer.</p>', '<p>To figure out by the end of my first semester, what discipline of engineering I would want to major in.</p>', 'Bravo', 'Cadet', '', '', NULL, NULL, 0),
