('Memorandum Standardization', '<p>All memorandums will now be submitted through the website unless otherwise specified. This includes all excused and unexcused PMT events.</p>\r\n<p>Memos will still be written formerly using the same template that can be found in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://onedrive.live.com/?authkey=%21AJPa0eTlsQ64xlg&amp;cid=3825622D1AC56C93&amp;id=3825622D1AC56C93%211011&amp;parId=3825622D1AC56C93%21967&amp;o=OneUp\">OneDrive.</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Steps to submit a memo:</p>\r\n<p>1. Under More, select&nbsp; \'View Event Attendance\'</p>\r\n<p>2. Select the event that was missed under \'Select Event\'; for normal memo submissions select \'Memo Submission\'</p>\r\n<p>3. Under \'Memo Reason\' select the reason why you missed the event or \'Non-Attendance\' for non-attendance related memos</p>\r\n<p>4. Enter only the LAST name of the cadet who requested the memo under \'For Cadet\'</p>\r\n<p>5. Attach a PDF of your memo including any doctors notes, do NOT submit any file type other than a PDF</p>', 7, '2020-01-10 05:05:01', NULL);
